summary: CPSC: I HAVE A BABY TREND CAR SEAT HYBRID 3 IN 1 MODEL # FB48417. AS I WAS TRYING TO BUCKLE MY CHILD IN THE CAR SEAT THE  CHEST CLIP BROKE. THIS IS NOT A CAR SEAT THAT IS USED HEAVILY. IT IS A SPARE THAT IS KEPT IN ANOTHER VEHICLE. IT CONCERNED M BECAUSE THE CLIP SEEMS TO NOT BE VERY STURDY TO WITHSTAND AN IMPACT   IF IT WERE TO OCCUR. *BF   UPDATED 06/28/2017*JS
